1.0.name: wordpress/pupul
1.0.description: Pupul is a simple, neat, clean, nice looking, fastest loading theme based on HTML, CSS & Aplau Framework for your WordPress site or blog. Use custom menu, custom logo, six widgets ( two sidebar widgets, four footer widgets, advertisement and analytics ready features with theme options.
